summary: I did a Bowsette fan red hair version with more muscular body; bikini inspired by cosplayer Jessica Nigri. Work done in MediBang...
body: I did a Bowsette fan red hair version with more muscular body; bikini inspired by cosplayer Jessica Nigri. Work done in MediBang Paint Pro on iPad Pro 1st gen. with Apple Pencil. MediBang Paint Pro is free to use on both desktop and mobile devices. I like the Clipping Mask and Protect Alpha, but wish MediBang would add masks to the layer so I can control the visibility with grayscale(Same as Photoshop). More info on Bowsette from Tokyosaurus: https://youtu.be/thDG7eNU2_Q

summary: In Super Mario Odyssey, the light coming from the Odyssey during certain parts of the game that take place at night is part of...
caption:
In Super Mario Odyssey, the light coming from the Odyssey during certain parts of the game that take place at night is part of the environment rather than dynamically tied to the ship. Note how there is a cone of light on the ground when the headlight is lit; however, when it is shuttered, the same cone of light remains even though it should disappear in response to the light going out.
Main Blog | Twitter | Patreon | Store | Source: myself, Super Mario Odyssey (Switch) on original hardware
